include the amounts necessary and said departments, boards,
SB141 INTRODUCED
2643 offices, commissions, and agencies are hereby directed to make
2644 the transfer of funds to the State Personnel Department in the
2645 amounts enumerated in the general appropriations act for the
2646 fiscal year ending September 30, 2027. All agencies and
