2729 Section 17. The State Superintendent of Education
2730 shall notify each local superintendent and finance officer of
2731 each local education agency by email regarding the
2732 availability and application process, including any required
2733 forms, for any available grant opportunities during FY 2027.
2734 The State Superintendent shall notify all members of the local
2735 legislative delegation five days prior to the announcement of
2736 any grant made to any entity located in the legislative
2737 jurisdiction. The five days prior notice requirement shall be
2738 waived in the event of a declared emergency. The Governor
2739 shall encourage the Department to disburse the funds provided
2740 herein on a nondiscriminatory basis.
2741 Section 18. Except as may be herein otherwise
2742 provided, amounts herein specifically appropriated shall be in
